dct_description_sm: © Ústřední správa geodézie a kartografie 1962. "Zpracoval a vytiski Kartografický a reprodukčni ústav Praze. Texty zpracoval kolektiv propag. oddél. n.p. Čedok." "D-04-40140". "C.v. 165-64". Includes a Czech and French index. Selected buildings are shown pictorially. Zpracovala Kartografie. Vytiskla Kartografia. Index for cultural centers, theaters, books about Prague and points of interest. Selected buildigns are illustrated. Verso: descriptions of Prague, index for hotels, restaurants, etc.
dct_publisher_sm: Praha : Ústřední správa geodézie a kartografie, [1962].
